          <h3>Best Overall Budget: Celestron SkyMaster 10x50</h3>
          <p><strong>Price:</strong> $50-$70 | <strong>Aperture:</strong> 50mm | <strong>Magnification:</strong> 10x | <strong>Field of View:</strong> 5.5° | <strong>Weight:</strong> 750g</p>

